We went here last Friday night and left hungry.
Part of it was because my in laws were in town and apparently eat like birds (which you wouldn't know from looking at them), but part of it was because you can't eat enough here to get full.
Don't get me wrong - every morsel of food I put in my mouth here was to die for.
