However, I'd like more than a bite.
This is a meal, not a strip tease.
The portions were ridiculously small.
Yes, tapas are small, but these were like tapas for ants.
I have never been to a tapas restaurant with portions this tiny.
I know I am from New Orleans where we eat way too much, but get real - people are normally hungry at dinner time!
